      "anno_id": 1,
      "text": " where  $U(\\phi)$  is a potential and  $p_{\\phi} = \\dot{\\phi} v$  is the momentum conjugate to the scalar field. From the equations of motion we find that the scalar field obeys a Klein-Gordon-like equation:",
      "line_with_spans": [
        {
          "category_type": "text_span",
          "poly": [
            217.4999999999999,
            1262.5,
