        1772.5,
        219.9999999999999,
        1772.5
      ],
      "ignore": false,
      "order": "15",
      "anno_id": 1,
      "text": " The ideal potential for an EU model has a plateau (i.e. an asymptote) at  $\\phi \\to -\\infty$  and a well with an absolute minimum at  $\\phi = \\phi_f$ ; it takes the form",
      "line_with_spans": [
        {
          "category_type": "text_span",
          "poly": [
            219.9999999999999,
            1630,
            1252.5,
            1630,
