      ],
      "ignore": false,
      "order": "27",
      "anno_id": 1,
      "text": " In this section we present a modified Heisenberg algebra, that in the classical limit translates to modified Poisson brackets, which is able to yield an EU-like solution without the need of much fine-tuning.",
